<body>
    <h1>Task 21 - RAD</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <h1 local-id=3D"d50d8f3db479" id=3D"Task21-RAD-1.Introduction">1. I=
ntroduction</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"4b2bfde8547e" id=3D"Task21-RAD-1.1Purpose">1.1 Purpose</h2>
<p local-id=3D"e56ada3f884c">The purpose of this document is to define the =
requirements for deploying a <strong>Hello World application on Azure App S=
ervice</strong>, mapping it to a <strong>custom domain using DNS records</s=
trong>, and analyzing <strong>SOA record details for DNS understanding</str=
ong>.</p>
<p local-id=3D"c5594a07324c">This document is intended for:</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"a743fa0acf29">DevOps Engineers</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"26683c1f9f40">Cloud Engineers</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"c414bca99fa4">Students and Interns</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"51959c0c200c">Project Evaluators</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2 local-id=3D"e6b592006faf" id=3D"Task21-RAD-1.2Scope">1.2 Scope</h2>
<p local-id=3D"73a3cfbdb2f3"><strong>Included in scope:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"b7fdb52533d5">Azure App Service creation and deployment</p><=
/li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"f1ba3039929b">Custom domain configuration</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"61e7b1cf3e3a">DNS record creation (CNAME, TXT)</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"5a1e69279d7e">Domain ownership validation</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"ae12ac77ce4c">SOA record inspection</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"8de5c02b47ff"><strong>Not included:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"17ce826e58d6">CI/CD pipeline setup</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"f26c07817b33">Advanced scaling or load balancing</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"e8a33129f89a">Security enhancements beyond basic DNS validat=
ion</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2 local-id=3D"7ea83f6bcc75" id=3D"Task21-RAD-1.3Definitions,Acronyms,andA=
bbreviations">1.3 Definitions, Acronyms, and Abbreviations</h2>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"1800" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"f=
d13f765-5b0f-46f4-a5de-229e1a1fd302" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"bab572527594">Term</p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"7eca3775075d">Meaning</p></th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"abc2e4cfc57d">DNS</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"fe2247ac5ff8">Domain Name System</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"287134e5d2a2">CNAME</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"832e5c6e39eb">Canonical Name Record</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"18b683bc953d">TXT</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"d65ee88777fa">Text Record</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"93e075c24ce8">SOA</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"8ec1eedcf9fc">Start of Authority</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"7a12ced7c987">Azure App Service</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"b1c959ac3073">Platform for hosting web apps</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<hr>
<h2 local-id=3D"9720f98242b3" id=3D"Task21-RAD-1.4References">1.4 Reference=
s</h2>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"ef54b800994a">Microsoft Azure Documentation</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"d2b204ecb48a">Azure App Service Docs</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"a78351813ebd">DNS RFC Standards</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2 local-id=3D"65df5469629b" id=3D"Task21-RAD-1.5Overview">1.5 Overview</h=
2>
<p local-id=3D"dec3c6b1f62a">This document includes:</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"06a9524b5347">Project overview and objectives</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"ac0a5d29bcd3">Functional and non-functional requirements</p>=
</li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"21e38f879d98">Use cases based on system design</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"e3547fce9af8">DNS validation and analysis</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h1 local-id=3D"106c0398f2d2" id=3D"Task21-RAD-2.ProjectOverview">2. Projec=
t Overview</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"9fbe7b7a1771" id=3D"Task21-RAD-2.1ProjectObjectives">2.1 Pr=
oject Objectives</h2>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"924aa6c8a867">Deploy a Hello World application on Azure</p><=
/li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"45f29e545a96">Configure a custom hostname</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"a2cf9ebd0ef4">Validate domain ownership using DNS</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"b0d9a8f2829a">Map domain using CNAME record</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"2072b3b69ce5">Analyze SOA record details</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2 local-id=3D"4a9ffb0cb5ce" id=3D"Task21-RAD-2.2BusinessGoals">2.2 Busine=
ss Goals</h2>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"bbcec582e1d8">Enable quick deployment using PaaS</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"2eba265cf07d">Improve domain-based access</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"24c56638191f">Ensure secure domain ownership validation</p><=
/li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"1ce0f87a5d47">Understand DNS working in cloud environments</=
p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2 local-id=3D"a9c9ec910bf7" id=3D"Task21-RAD-2.3Background">2.3 Backgroun=
d</h2>
<p local-id=3D"f0af9fc55601">ABC Technologies wants to host applications on=
 Azure and connect them with custom domains.</p>
<p local-id=3D"c41828bd432f">DNS is essential for:</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"90667bedcd24">Mapping domain names to services</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"be88e3151e57">Verifying ownership</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"c83be5456749">Managing domain routing</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"ccf40a29e181">This project helps in understanding both <stro=
ng>deployment and DNS integration</strong>.</p>
<hr>
<h2 local-id=3D"5596f73f356e" id=3D"Task21-RAD-2.4Constraints">2.4 Constrai=
nts</h2>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"600fe6c73def">Domain availability required</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"da0af7e40a16">DNS propagation delay</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"b94a8a545f39">Azure subscription required</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"645eac37b77c">Manual DNS configuration</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h1 local-id=3D"d24333273fa7" id=3D"Task21-RAD-3.FunctionalRequirements">3.=
 Functional Requirements</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"a5208b81bb07" id=3D"Task21-RAD-3.1UseCaseDiagram">3.1 Use C=
ase Diagram</h2><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-cente=
r-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size"><img class=3D"confluence-embedde=
d-image image-center" alt=3D"Untitled Diagram.drawio (19)-20260327-121049.p=
ng" width=3D"468" loading=3D"lazy" src=3D"84d4353f4c612ec5d0e9b8ccfb8aa6398=
41869f02e05ef7e3669b2575f01177f" data-image-src=3D"https://iamops.atlassian=
.net/wiki/download/attachments/1886289945/Untitled%20Diagram.drawio%20(19)-=
20260327-121049.png?version=3D1&amp;modificationDate=3D1774613593880&amp;ca=
cheVersion=3D1&amp;api=3Dv2" data-height=3D"481" data-width=3D"1014" data-u=
nresolved-comment-count=3D"0" data-linked-resource-id=3D"1908834320" data-l=
