0d-89ad-4980-be3c-fd896afd84a1" data-media-type=3D"file" height=3D"222"></s=
pan>
<h2 local-id=3D"84a2a260a740" id=3D"Task21-RAD-3.2UseCases">3.2 Use Cases</=
h2>
<hr>
<h3 local-id=3D"e8a2dd5d5a1d" id=3D"Task21-RAD-3.2.1UseCase1:CreateAzureApp=
Service&amp;DeployApp">3.2.1 Use Case 1: Create Azure App Service &amp; Dep=
loy App</h3>
<p local-id=3D"945edcce575e"><strong>Description:</strong><br>
Deploy a Hello World application on Azure App Service.</p>
<p local-id=3D"4f7dbb4218a1"><strong>Actors:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"2e5c730971a2">DevOps Engineer</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"7061077d99f8"><strong>Preconditions:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"33722f638ce2">Azure account available</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"5caf5cb8e45b"><strong>Postconditions:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"29fb736f9aa5">Application accessible via default URL</p></li=
>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"85595722090e"><strong>Flow of Events:</strong></p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p local-id=3D"4efee06eefef">Create Azure App Service</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"d03d6e245d83">Deploy application</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"a7695cac3007">Start the service</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"40aeff97fd75">Verify access via default URL</p></li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"908968979b00"><strong>Alternative Flows:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"9b46daf2d7ba">Deployment failure =E2=86=92 check logs</p></l=
i>
</ul>
<hr>
<h3 local-id=3D"d85f2aa7b530" id=3D"Task21-RAD-3.2.2UseCase2:ConfigureCusto=
mHostname">3.2.2 Use Case 2: Configure Custom Hostname</h3>
<p local-id=3D"7b01faa43f40"><strong>Description:</strong><br>
Link custom domain to Azure App Service.</p>
<p local-id=3D"39388cbc7a34"><strong>Actors:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"85bda2f0f803">DevOps Engineer</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"a6a58104e65d"><strong>Preconditions:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"885a23d4895b">App deployed</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"93acc8f47b8d">Domain available</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"5ba73975e13f"><strong>Postconditions:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"f4d0a5d8ac40">Custom domain mapped successfully</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"85cf9de85b21"><strong>Flow of Events:</strong></p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p local-id=3D"d3b43469222b">Add custom domain in Azure</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"e29cb454e557">Enter domain name</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"852f8cbd9c87">Verify domain ownership</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"0d3921d497c9">Bind domain</p></li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"668e00fac713"><strong>Alternative Flows:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"0d791d4781d0">Domain verification fails</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h3 local-id=3D"2dee76fd2547" id=3D"Task21-RAD-3.2.3UseCase3:CreateDNSRecor=
ds(CNAME,TXT)">3.2.3 Use Case 3: Create DNS Records (CNAME, TXT)</h3>
<p local-id=3D"b39d40f1ac6d"><strong>Description:</strong><br>
Create required DNS records for mapping and verification.</p>
<p local-id=3D"540b12b41dab"><strong>Actors:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"f78ee167858f">DevOps Engineer</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"1b63889f3861"><strong>Preconditions:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"2df4ae7918bd">Access to DNS provider</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"ad7f1577fa06"><strong>Postconditions:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"00024ce691da">DNS records configured</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"46eeeb259c61"><strong>Flow of Events:</strong></p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p local-id=3D"f687d7449e27">Create CNAME record =E2=86=92 points to Azure =
URL</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"8635a4808976">Create TXT record =E2=86=92 verification</p></=
li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"6477c57369e9">Save DNS records</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"cc65510f069c">Wait for propagation</p></li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"f48b5ab2347c"><strong>Alternative Flows:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"15500039a65b">Incorrect record =E2=86=92 mapping fails</p></=
li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h3 local-id=3D"eb78c6ac2067" id=3D"Task21-RAD-3.2.4UseCase4:ValidateDomain=
Ownership&amp;DNSResolution">3.2.4 Use Case 4: Validate Domain Ownership &a=
mp; DNS Resolution</h3>
<p local-id=3D"f860f822774a"><strong>Description:</strong><br>
Verify domain mapping and DNS functionality.</p>
<p local-id=3D"a3ce941ebceb"><strong>Actors:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"df357e499ea8">DevOps Engineer</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"da0b86172164">End User</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"ad97883efaba"><strong>Preconditions:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"d4239fea2bb2">DNS records created</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"5f0eabe4edad"><strong>Postconditions:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"012b57dd0500">Domain resolves correctly</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"d083f220c7c4"><strong>Flow of Events:</strong></p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p local-id=3D"7f03b89f250c">Check DNS resolution</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"585a8b691cbe">Verify TXT record</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"c01792f70928">Access domain</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"0663b0b80a0b">Confirm app loads</p></li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"f0ae1147004d"><strong>Alternative Flows:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"7b9a77117dcd">DNS delay =E2=86=92 wait and retry</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h3 local-id=3D"11712118af7c" id=3D"Task21-RAD-3.2.5UseCase5:InspectSOAReco=
rd">3.2.5 Use Case 5: Inspect SOA Record</h3>
<p local-id=3D"e8ecf4496fb4"><strong>Description:</strong><br>
Analyze SOA record to understand DNS zone configuration.</p>
<p local-id=3D"7e279f5d8e89"><strong>Actors:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"454d425e9535">DevOps Engineer</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"f38f8f11ce96"><strong>Preconditions:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"b6089e1fbe2c">Domain configured</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"a75c6ea2d815"><strong>Postconditions:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"8baf9b343f48">SOA fields documented and explained</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"e2024aa885d8"><strong>Flow of Events:</strong></p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p local-id=3D"a7993261e827">Query SOA record</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"5eefc937c327">Extract values</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"bd55dedafa73">Analyze fields</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"be3a3c995dd9">Document explanation</p></li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"cc7b322c75a9"><strong>Alternative Flows:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"ea703354f33b">Incorrect query</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h1 local-id=3D"8c19bcb7601f" id=3D"Task21-RAD-4.Non-FunctionalRequirements=
">4. Non-Functional Requirements</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"fd1b3aa1cb42" id=3D"Task21-RAD-4.1PerformanceRequirements">=
4.1 Performance Requirements</h2>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"e7c3969aa7fa">Fast application response</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"77c81b51e30a">Efficient DNS resolution</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"efe6d01d9cf3">Minimal delay</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2 local-id=3D"8a7c7d2e9f02" id=3D"Task21-RAD-4.2SecurityRequirements">4.2=
 Security Requirements</h2>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"b8b43d820649">Domain ownership verification via TXT</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"218ac5ae892c">Secure Azure access</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"d1e553cf26e5">Controlled DNS updates</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2 local-id=3D"f75a8c4655c5" id=3D"Task21-RAD-4.3UsabilityRequirements">4.=
3 Usability Requirements</h2>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"688d296b6e32">Easy domain access</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"c5c971465018">Simple Azure UI</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"6d5b4a22401d">Clear DNS configuration</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2 local-id=3D"9a1aa6e698ee" id=3D"Task21-RAD-4.4ReliabilityRequirements">=
4.4 Reliability Requirements</h2>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"ec4cd2ab0023">High uptime via Azure App Service</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"8e83eabb72df">Reliable DNS resolution</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"d2ccfd3eec14">Consistent domain mapping</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2 local-id=3D"4e91b312295c" id=3D"Task21-RAD-4.5ComplianceRequirements">4=
.5 Compliance Requirements</h2>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"32509c5d6fd8">Follow Azure best practices</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"3eb6a2ff9bd4">Secure DNS configurations</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"50eba07ec277">Proper validation process</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h1 local-id=3D"ca8807495eb6" id=3D"Task21-RAD-5.AssumptionsandDependencies=
">5. Assumptions and Dependencies</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"41bd5b12fdec" id=3D"Task21-RAD-5.1Assumptions">5.1 Assumpti=
ons</h2>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"630d2c329637">Domain name is available</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"da143fbbce74">Azure services accessible</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"c027058ced1a">Internet connectivity available</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2 local-id=3D"709e23acd49b" id=3D"Task21-RAD-5.2Dependencies">5.2 Depende=
ncies</h2>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"8cc7364a420d">Azure App Service</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"dbc24fbfd897">DNS provider (GoDaddy, Namecheap, etc.)</p></l=
i>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"4a9162f17f8e">Domain registrar</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h1 local-id=3D"f36e129f210d" id=3D"Task21-RAD-6.RiskAnalysis">6. Risk Anal=
ysis</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"02c1f69ecdb3" id=3D"Task21-RAD-6.1RiskIdentification">6.1 R=
isk Identification</h2>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"7e9ce9f48bc8">DNS propagation delay</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"1fdf7f100ac1">Incorrect DNS records</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"b772057a1170">Domain verification failure</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"12e3924bfa2b">Deployment issues</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2 local-id=3D"b4808536baa9" id=3D"Task21-RAD-6.2RiskMitigation">6.2 Risk =
Mitigation</h2>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"656bb2520c8e">Verify DNS entries carefully</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"7013f9c9163f">Wait for propagation</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"e9d7b1c2fa7a">Use DNS tools</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"d071f50a764b">Check Azure logs</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
